snippet.title: Freelancer Simulator 2: Startup and Gamedeveloper life simulator [Gameplay Promo]
snippet.description:
Join to the Freelancer Simulator 2 - mobile idle life simulator for Android. Create your own startup, build apps and games, hire new employers, open new offices and invest in other companies!

Download for Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ocugine.freelancer2free
